    "description": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">At the start of a conflict, you may spend up to </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>【</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>SL × 5</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>】 </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Mind Points. For every 5 Mind Points you spend this way, choose one option: choose a creature you can see and the GM reveals one of their </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>Traits</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">; </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">or </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">name a damage type and choose a creature you can see, and the GM reveals that creature's </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>Affinity </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">towards that damage type.</span> </p><hr /><p>Skill Level <strong>1</strong> - <strong>@LOSS[5 mp]</strong></p><p>Skill Level <strong>2</strong> - <strong>@LOSS[10 mp]</strong></p><p>Skill Level <strong>3</strong> - <strong>@LOSS[15 mp]</strong></p><p>Skill Level <strong>4</strong> - <strong>@LOSS[20 mp]</strong></p><p>Skill Level <strong>5</strong> - <strong>@LOSS[25 mp]</strong></p><p>Skill Level <strong>6</strong> - <strong>@LOSS[30 mp]</strong></p>",
